/* ════════ ẨN element CŨ duplicate trong article cũ ════════ */
/* Giữ visible: predict widget X COIN (#predictWidget) + AI Insights widget */
/* Ẩn: score row, BLV chips, info aside, SEO article cũ, others list cards */
